name: Photo Slideshow Template for After Effects
description:
This Photo Slideshow Template for After Effects, is Perfect for weddings, birthdays, anniversaries, showing off holiday photos, or any occasion you can think of!

Here's why you will love this Easy to Customise After Effects Template
• It supports 1080p, 720p, 480p. • Up to 21 image / video placeholders (easy to add more, so as many photos as you like!). • Text placeholders for each image. • Title and subtitle for each photo set. • No plugins required. • Easy to add more photo sets • Instantly and easily change the look by using the colour adjustment layer. • Help File Included. • After Effects CS6 or higher. • 25 fps.
This Template is Perfect for Any Occasion!
No Plugins Required Because this After Effects Template doesn't uses any plugins, you can spend less time setting up, and more time creating that perfect photo gallery movie.
Instantly change the look a feel Colours can be Adjusted very easily using a single adjustment layer. and photos are easy to insert and replace.
